PrintMoney: SaaS Template
Project Overview
Velocity is a comprehensive SaaS starter template designed to help developers ship their ideas blazingly fast. The template provides a solid foundation with pre-configured, production-ready components, enabling developers to focus on building their unique features rather than spending time on boilerplate code and infrastructure setup.
Tech Stack
Frontend

Next.js: React framework with server-side rendering, API routes, and optimized build system
TypeScript: For type safety and better developer experience
Tailwind CSS: Utility-first CSS framework for rapid UI development
shadcn/ui: Reusable UI components built with Radix UI and Tailwind

Backend & Data

Next.js API Routes: Serverless functions for backend logic
Neon Postgres: Serverless PostgreSQL database with automatic scaling
Drizzle ORM: TypeScript ORM for database interactions with a focus on type safety
Database Schema: Includes common models for users, teams, subscriptions, and more

Authentication

Better Auth: Complete authentication solution with:

Email/password authentication
OAuth providers (Google, GitHub, etc.)
Magic link login
MFA support
Session management
Role-based access control



Payments & Billing

Stripe Integration: Complete subscription management

Multiple pricing tiers
Free trials
Usage-based billing options
Invoice management
Payment failure handling
Subscription lifecycle webhooks



Monitoring & Analytics

Sentry: Error tracking and performance monitoring

Real-time error reporting
User impact analysis
Performance monitoring
Release tracking


PostHog: Product analytics and feature flags

User event tracking
Conversion funnels
Session recordings
A/B testing
Feature flags for gradual rollouts